---
title: Easy Baked Mumbai Veggie Curry with Rapid Rice & Peanuts
description: This quickly prepped and creamy Mumbai-style curry will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night. It's filled to
the brim with bright veggies, fluffy rice and finished with a sprinkling of flair from roasted peanuts.
